{"lastModified":1773327658905,"uri":"c::7579706445::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nLa Pellegrina 1 is a remarkable motor yacht, crafted by the renowned Chantier Naval Couach and delivered in 2012 as the flagship model of the Couach 164' series. In 2024, she underwent an extensive refit, elevating her luxurious features, performance, and overall allure, ensuring she remains at the pinnacle of modern yachting excellence. With her striking design and exceptional craftsmanship, she stands as a true symbol of luxury and sophistication on the water. Her interior features an expansive, Open-plan main saloon that is bathed in natural light, courtesy of the full-height panoramic windows. The saloon is elegantly furnished with a generous seating area for relaxation, while a refined dining area, separated by a sleek island credenza, offers a perfect setting for formal dining. The main deck houses a distinguished VIP suite, designed to offer guests a 180-degree panoramic view, enhancing the sense of openness and connection with the surrounding environment. The Master Suite, located on the upper deck, is an epitome of comfort and style, featuring a full-beam layout and a private aft deck with a U-shaped lounging area—ideal for both private relaxation and entertaining in a serene setting. La Pellegrina 1 accommodates up to 12 guests in six luxurious cabins. The four guest suites located on the lower deck each provide exquisite comfort, with three offering queen-sized beds and one featuring twin beds, all designed to ensure a restful and refined atmosphere. The exterior spaces of the yacht are expansive and thoughtfully designed across three decks. The sundeck is an inviting area for sunbathing, equipped with comfortable sunbeds, and also features a spa jacuzzi for ultimate relaxation. A central round dining table and a wet bar on the sundeck create an ideal environment for alfresco dining and entertaining. The large swimming platform at the stern offers direct access to the water, providing a perfect spot for unwinding or engaging in water activities.","blueprint":{"name":"LA PELLEGRINA 1","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::57a260b0-0bde-11f0-9eef-3fd8575e88be/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8cb12ec0-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8cd83ec0-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8cd83ec1-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8ce55e20-0bdf-11f0-b4c1-2df472b8cea4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8cdfdfe0-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8ce277f0-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8ce4c1e0-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8ccfda50-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8cd77b70-0bdf-11f0-b4c1-2df472b8cea4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8cd6b820-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8cd7a280-0bdf-11f0-b5d8-3d2c0509acbf/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8ca8ca50-0bdf-11f0-b04e-c3983bbd418b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7772-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8cd8